text: Fairbanks is an unincorporated community in Ouachita Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located along Louisiana Highway 134 near U.S. Route 165, north-northeast of downtown Monroe. Fairbanks has a post office with ZIP code 71240. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Ouachita Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
title: Fairbanks, Louisiana
